    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is strictly a project car or a source for parts. It currently does not start, and the engine requires a complete overhaul. The body shows significant rust and several large dents, while the interior has sustained heavy wear and tear over the years. This is an ideal purchase for someone with the mechanical expertise to perform a full restoration or for those needing specific components for another build.",
